```{r}
library(tidyverse)
example_df = tibble
sample=runif(10, min=0, max=5)
logical = sample > 2
vec_char = c("My", "name", "is", "Jiabei", "and", "I", "am", "a", "graduate", "student")
vec_factor = factor(c("male", "male", "male", "male", "male", "female", "female", "female", "female", "female"))
mean(sample)
mean(logical)
mean(vec_char)
mean(vec_factor)
```
